author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-MolMed Q1 Net Loss Narrows to EUR 1.2 Mln
text:
May 14 (Reuters) - MolMed:
* REPORTED ON FRIDAY Q1 NET LOSS OF EUR 1.2 MLN VS LOSS EUR 3.7 MLN YEAR AGO
* Q1 OPERATING REVENUE OF EUR 5.8 MLN VS EUR 4.4 MLN YEAR AGO
